    {
      "id": "65fce1c7cd81ab7648c69d103e4681cdcad5daed",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 888,
        "name": "Thomas Stibor",
        "email": "thomas@stibor.net",
        "username": "t.stibor@gsi.de"
      },
      "date": "2022-04-22 12:20:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(3 comments)\n\nAndreas, thanks for the hints and tips. I fixed all the issues and switched\nto the same syntax as e.g. 'ls' command.\n\nRegarding adding manual pages for hsm_{archive,restore,release,...}\nI think it makes sense to create a new and separate manual file, e.g.\nlfs-hsm_operations.1 because hsm_{archive,restore,release,...} share\nthe same options:\n\n[--filelist FILELIST] [--data DATA] <file> ...\n[--filelist FILELIST] [--data DATA] [--archive NUM] <file> ...\n\nrather than packing that also in lfs-hsm.1?\n\nProbably it would be good to do that in a new LU-XXXXX PR?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
