      },
      "date": "2022-04-22 19:53:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nRather than \"lfs-hsm_operations\", which is not a real command, it would be better to pick one of the actual command names, like \"lfs-hsm_archive.1\" and then link the other commands there, and also add them to the SEE ALSO section in lfs-hsm.1. The only reason lfs-hsm.1 is OK is because this matches the actual command name, with sub-options.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
